---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle-Honey Pork Chops with Garlic Veggies and Sour Cream Smashed Potatoes
description: Smoky sweetness is the name of this calorie conscious meal! A craveable combination of chipotle and honey is spooned over smoky chops and served with wholesome sides of tangy smashed potatoes and tender-crisp veggies. It's an all around win-win!

